title: East Osgiltath Surrounded: Defense of Men and Elves - Third Age Total War Mod Gameplay
description:
BATTLE STARTS AT: 5:48
Men and Elves have united once agin to defend East Osgiliath.  Mordor, Isengard, and Orcs of Gundabad surround the city from every direction.  The only way of survival is to fight there way out! Enjoy the Siege Battle :D

Third Age: Reforged is a Sub Mod for Third Age Total War!

If you enjoyed the video don't forget to Like and Leave a comment :D
